{
    "attributes": {
        "action": "Mandatory three-month prison sentence for damage to war memorials or statues",
        "additional_details": "I feel that current offences and associated sentences do not go far enough, and this will ensure that people guilty of damaging war memorials or statutes face a suitable punishment.\r\n \r\nIt should also mean that those that do carry out these abhorrent acts will know they face a prison sentence if found guilty.\r\n",
        "background": "We want the Government to make damaging war memorials or statutes a specific criminal offence, with a mandatory three-month prison sentence.",
